an%20connection%20can't%20be%20beat.%20It%20encouraged%20founders%20of%20growth-stage%20companies%20to%20lean%20into%20events%20%E2%80%94%20from%20intimate%20gatherings%20with%20potential%20buyers%20to%20larger%20industry%20events%20%E2%80%94%20as%20a%20means%20of%20connecting%20with%20customers%20and%20scaling%20demand.%20This%20will%20help%20companies%20%26quot%3Bstand%20out%20in%20a%20world%20increasingly%20flooded%20with%20digital%2C%20AI-powered%20outreach%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20memo%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227b436487-040e-4362-bef6-b9b7866d8ecd%5C%22%3ERead%20the%20letter%20Insight%20shared%20with%20execs.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ELoyal%20Field%20Notes%20readers%2C%20as%202025%20approaches%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20share%20some%20insights%20on%20high-impact%20strategies%20for%20scaling%20your%20company%20effectively%20in%20the%20coming%20year.%20Our%20Insight%20Onsite%20team%2C%20made%20up%20of%20130%2B%20professionals%20with%20deep%20operational%20expertise%2C%20is%20here%20to%20support%20your%20growth%20journey%20and%20help%20you%20capitalize%20on%20opportunities%20across%20AI%2C%20go-to-market%20(GTM)%20strategies%2C%20talent%2C%20and%20beyond.%20We%20hope%20you%20find%20the%20following%20helpful%20and%20as%20always%2C%20reach%20out%20to%20your%20Portfolio%20Manager%20or%20Onsite%20contact%20if%20you%20have%20any%20questions.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch4%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ef102a3b-ef8e-4c6a-bdbd-7470482e2348%5C%22%3EThe%20shift%20to%20AI%20is%20imminent%20and%20leads%20to%20advanced%20scaling%20and%20sophistication%20among%20entrepreneurs%3C%2Fh4%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAI%20was%20the%20buzzword%20of%202024%20and%20isn't%20going%20anywhere%20in%20the%20next%20year.%20AI%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20drive%20the%20next%20wave%20of%20innovation%2C%20offering%20growth%20opportunities.%20For%20early-stage%20companies%20looking%20to%20scale%20with%20AI%20in%202025%2C%20the%20focus%20should%20be%20on%20high-impact%20applications%20that%20drive%20efficiency%20and%20empower%20teams.%20Key%20areas%20for%20immediate%20gains%20include%20developer%20productivity%2C%20quality%20assurance%2Ftesting%2C%20and%20marketing%20content%20creation.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAutomation%20can%20simplify%20repetitive%20tasks%20across%20functions%3A%20for%20developers%2C%20it%20means%20faster%20code%20generation%20and%20reviews%3B%20for%20marketing%2C%20automated%20copy%20and%20content%20testing%20enhance%20engagement%20strategies%3B%20and%20for%20customer%20support%2C%20AI-powered%20tools%20streamline%20response%20times%20and%20improve%20knowledge%20management.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETalent%20acquisition%20and%20sales%20also%20benefit%20from%20AI%2C%20with%20tools%20like%20%26quot%3BCopilot%26quot%3B%20that%20assist%20in%20candidate%20research%2C%20onboarding%2C%20and%20customer%20relationship%20management%E2%80%94enhancing%20personalization%2C%20productivity%2C%20and%20scalability.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETracking%20progress%20and%20refining%20AI%20strategies%20over%20time%20enables%20companies%20to%20scale%20efficiently%2C%20positioning%20them%20for%20sustainable%20growth%20and%20a%20competitive%20edge%20in%20the%20market.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch4%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2295a01d20-2bfb-4703-97cf-2a2753eb93c9%5C%22%3EFocus%20on%20leveraging%20emerging%20AI%20technologies%3C%2Fh4%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20idea%20of%20incorporating%20generative%20AI%20(GenAI)%20into%20companies%20can%20be%20daunting%20but%20it%20also%20has%20the%20potential%20to%20impact%20every%20function%20of%20a%20business.%20In%20a%20recent%20portfolio%20company%20survey%2C%20we%20found%20that%2072%25%20of%20portfolio%20companies%20are%20using%20Artificial%20Intelligence%2C%20with%2036%25%20of%20those%20companies%20creating%20a%20net%20new%20budget%20for%20those%20initiatives.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETo%20scale%20effectively%20with%20AI%20in%202025%2C%20early-stage%20companies%20should%20prioritize%20practical%20GenAI%20use%20cases%20that%20can%20yield%20high%20impact%20in%20areas%20like%20knowledge%20management%2C%20content%20generation%2C%20and%20customer%20insights.%20GenAI%20can%20enable%20efficient%20product%20development%20by%20automating%20tasks%20such%20as%20coding%2C%20design%20and%20rapid%20prototyping%2C%20leading%20to%20faster%20market%20entry%20and%20broader%20product%20variety.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIn%20market%20research%2C%20GenAI%20supports%20data-driven%20decisions%20by%20analyzing%20unstructured%20data%20sets%2C%20including%20customer%20interviews%20and%20competitor%20reviews%2C%20to%20reveal%20actionable%20insights.%20Additionally%2C%20for%20go-to-market%20(GTM)%20efforts%2C%20AI%20can%20streamline%20lead%20scoring%2C%20personalize%20customer%20engagement%2C%20and%20optimize%20sales%20campaigns%2C%20making%20the%20process%20scalable%20and%20significantly%20enhancing%20customer%20satisfaction%20and%20loyalty.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAI-driven%20automation%20presents%20a%20huge%20opportunity%20to%20boost%20productivity%20and%20streamline%20operations.%20As%20AI%20assistants%20and%20GenAI%20continue%20evolving%2C%20founders%20should%20adopt%20a%20%26quot%3Bcrawl%2C%20walk%2C%20run%26quot%3B%20approach%E2%80%94starting%20with%20simpler%20automated%20tasks%20and%20gradually%20incorporating%20more%20advanced%20workflows.%20Embracing%20a%20%26quot%3Bhuman-in-the-loop%26quot%3B%20framework%2C%20which%20combines%20AI%20with%20human%20oversight%2C%20will%20be%20essential%20as%20these%20systems%20are%20still%20maturing.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETo%20differentiate%20themselves%2C%20founders%20should%20focus%20on%20creating%20unique%2C%20data-driven%20workflows%20that%20add%20clear%20value%20and%20improve%20user%20experience%2C%20setting%20their%20businesses%20up%20for%20sustainable%20growth%20in%20an%20AI-enhanced%20market.%20We%20created%20a%20blog%20post%20exploring%20this%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insightpartners.com%2Fideas%2Fai-agents-disrupting-automation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Etopic%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20earlier%20this%20spring.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EScale%20your%20GTM%20engine%20on%20strong%20foundations%20and%20personalized%20engagement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFor%20early-stage%20founders%2C%20especially%20B2B%20SaaS%20companies%2C%20aiming%20to%20scale%20effectively%20in%202025%2C%20ensuring%20GTM%20strategy%20and%20engine%20works%20before%20you%20scale%20is%20critical.%20Once%20you%20have%20Product%20Market%20Fit%20(PMF)%20it's%20critical%20to%20continue%20to%20validate%20that%20your%20product%20creates%20real%2C%20differentiated%20value%20for%20your%20buyers%20(and%20that%20your%20messaging%20effectively%20communicates%20this).%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIt's%20not%20just%20about%20having%20a%20great%20product%20with%20cutting-edge%20features.%20Having%20a%20customer-centric%20mindset%20is%20key%3B%20products%20that%20solve%20a%20pressing%20problem%2C%20resonate%20authentically%2C%20and%20are%20easy%20to%20use%20will%20drive%20organic%20word-of-mouth%20and%20advocacy%2C%20which%20are%20priceless%20(and%20cost-effective)%20assets%20for%20growth.%20Add%20in%20high%20retention%20rates%20from%20strong%20PMF%20and%20effective%20onboarding%20and%20you've%20got%20the%20foundation%20for%20efficient%2C%20sustainable%20scaling.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFor%20growth%20stage%20companies%20and%20beyond%2C%20it's%20key%20to%20scale%20demand%20on%20top%20of%20this%20foundation%20by%20leaning%20back%20into%20events%20and%20in%20person%20connection.%20Look%20to%20personal%2C%20high-impact%20engagements%20to%20stand%20out%20in%20a%20world%20increasingly%20flooded%20with%20digital%2C%20AI-powered%20outreach.%20Companies%20can%20build%20meaningful%20connections%20and%20gain%20firsthand%20insights%20into%20their%20audience%20needs%20through%20hosting%20intimate%20gatherings%20with%20target%20buyers%20or%20attending%20larger%20industry%20events.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAI-powered%20outreach%20can't%20be%20ignored%20though%20%E2%80%93%20just%20don't%20expect%20AI%20to%20do%20it%20all%20for%20you.%20It's%20imperative%20to%20first%20find%20a%20battle-tested%20approach%20that%20works%2C%20and%20then%20augment%20it%20with%20AI%20to%20help%20scale%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3Epersonalized%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%20outreach%20efficiently.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKnow%20and%20understand%20your%20brand%20to%20hire%20key%20talent%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EIn%202025%2C%20early-stage%20founders%20need%20to%20approach%20talent%20acquisition%20with%20a%20compelling%20and%20cohesive%20narrative%20that%20highlights%20the%20unique%20value%20and%20culture%20of%20their%20company.%20Given%20the%20competitive%20landscape%2C%20your%20company's%20story%20should%20resonate%20through%20every%20touchpoint%2C%20especially%20the%20company%20website%20and%20the%20CEO's%20personal%20brand.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ECandidates%20are%20increasingly%20thorough%2C%20relying%20not%20only%20on%20public%20content%20but%20also%20on%20personal%20reference%20checks%20to%20understand%20a%20company's%20values%20and%20trajectory.%20A%20well-defined%2C%20authentic%20narrative%20that%20reflects%20both%20the%20mission%20and%20culture%20of%20the%20company%20can%20attract%20high-caliber%20talent%20by%20demonstrating%20transparency%2C%20stability%2C%20and%20alignment%20with%20employee%20priorities.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EManaging%20relationships%20effectively%20with%20candidates%E2%80%94even%20those%20not%20selected%20immediately%E2%80%94will%20be%20equally%20essential.%20With%20top%20talent%20in%20high%20demand%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20view%20every%20interaction%20as%20part%20of%20an%20ongoing%20relationship%3B%20a%20candidate%20who%20may%20not%20be%20the%20right%20fit%20today%20could%20become%20an%20ideal%20match%20as%20the%20company%20evolves.%20Keeping%20doors%20open%20with%20a%20gracious%20and%20professional%20approach%20to%20rejections%20can%20foster%20goodwill%2C%20making%20it%20easier%20to%20reconnect%20with%20talented%20individuals%20down%20the%20line.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EBy%20cultivating%20a%20respectful%20and%20thoughtful%20hiring%20process%2C%20founders%20can%20build%20a%20network%20of%20potential%20future%20hires%20who%20feel%20positively%20about%20the%20brand%2C%20regardless%20of%20the%20immediate%20outcome.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvc-firm-insight-partners-how-to-incorporate-generative-ai-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732785061000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F667c86bf50b021b5cae9c6e9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvc-firm-insight-partners-how-to-incorporate-generative-ai-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Insight%20Partners%2C%20a%20prominent%20venture%20capital%20firm%2C%20advises%20companies%20to%20take%20a%20%26quot%3Bcrawl%2C%20walk%2C%20run%26quot%3B%20approach%20to%20incorporating%20generative%20AI.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mrussell%40businessinsider.com%20(Melia%20Russell)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvc-firm-insight-partners-how-to-incorporate-generative-ai-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20avoid%20fighting%20over%20politics%20this%20Thanksgiving%20without%20ruining%20your%20meal%20%26amp%3Bmdash%3B%26amp%3Bnbsp%3Bor%20relationships%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Close%20up%20of%20Thanksgiving%20stuffed%20turkey%20on%20dining%20table%20with%20family%20in%20the%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67450de99f2901eb6036d247%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFour%20communications%20professionals%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20preparation%2C%20perspective%2C%20and%20personal%20boundaries%20are%20key%20to%20a%20drama-free%20Thanksgiving.%3Cp%3Eskynesher%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EHoliday%20gatherings%20are%20ripe%20for%20conflicts%20over%20politics%2C%20relationships%2C%20social%20issues%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EPreparation%2C%20a%20curious%20perspective%2C%20and%20personal%20boundaries%20help%20when%20navigating%20arguments.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFour%20communication%20experts%20shared%20their%20tips%20for%20keeping%20the%20holiday%20festivities%20peaceful%20this%20year.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20this%20year%20you're%20headed%20into%20Thanksgiving%20dinner%20with%20a%20pit%20in%20your%20stomach%2C%20worrying%20that%20your%20Great%20Aunt%20Karen%20will%20say%20something%20that'll%20set%20the%20whole%20family%20on%20a%20course%20toward%20WWIII%2C%20worry%20no%20longer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20get%20caught%20in%20a%20political%20debate%20or%20battle%20of%20wits%20with%20your%20friends%20or%20extended%20family%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0if%20you%20don't%20want%20to.%20With%20tips%20from%20communications%20professionals%20who%20know%20precisely%20how%20to%20navigate%20tension-filled%20conversations%20and%20come%20out%20the%20other%20side%20peacefully%20this%20holiday%20season%2C%20if%20you%20prefer%2C%20you%20can%20keep%20things%20light.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20talked%20to%20four%20communications%20professionals%20specializing%20in%20relationships%2C%20conflict%2C%20and%20negotiation%3A%20a%20professor%20of%20debate%2C%20a%20licensed%20clinical%20mental%20health%20counselor%20supervisor%2C%20a%20national%20speaker%20who%20helps%20people%20negotiate%20business%20deals%20and%20address%20conflict%20at%20work%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%20diversity%2C%20equity%2C%20and%20inclusion%20consultant.%20Here's%20what%20they%20say%20are%20the%20best%20ways%20to%20avoid%20clashing%20with%20your%20family%20at%20your%20end-of-year%20festivities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229582df98-e943-47c4-a04d-3de8cca3284c%5C%22%3EBe%20prepared%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20do%20when%20we%20bring%20our%20significant%20others%20or%20some%20of%20our%20friends%20to%20dinner%2C%20right%20before%20we%20go%20in%2C%20we%20say%20something%20like%20a%20disclaimer%2C%26quot%3B%20Risha%20Grant%2C%20an%20international%20speaker%20and%20DEI%20consultant%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20We%20warn%20them%20that%20our%20grandmother%2C%20uncle%2C%20or%20other%20extended%20family%20is%20%26quot%3Bfrom%20a%20different%20generation%2C%20so%20they%20may%20say%20something%20offensive%20%E2%80%94%20just%20ignore%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20instead%20of%20giving%20that%20disclaimer%20to%20your%20guests%2C%20Grant%20suggests%20giving%20it%20to%20your%20loved%20ones%20ahead%20of%20time.%20Instead%20of%20asking%20your%20guests%20to%20let%20things%20slide%2C%20try%20telling%20your%20problematic%20relative%20that%20this%20year%2C%20you'd%20rather%20keep%20things%20neutral.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20explicitly%20spelling%20out%20that%20the%20family%20is%20trying%20to%20avoid%20hot-button%20conversations%20this%20year%2C%20you%20set%20expectations%20for%20everyone%20and%20put%20yourself%20in%20the%20driver's%20seat%2C%20settling%20some%20of%20the%20anxiety%20that%20comes%20with%20thinking%20about%20what%20might%20happen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20can%20have%20that%20conversation%20beforehand%2C%20and%20let%20your%20loved%20ones%20know%20that%20dinner%20is%20not%20the%20time%20to%20have%20that%20conversation%2C%20you%20can%20try%20to%20head%20it%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20Grant%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22da800d23-13e1-4743-ae0c-599590c9dd81%5C%22%3ESet%20and%20keep%20firm%20boundaries%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20when%20Uncle%20Brandon%20just%20%3Cem%3Ehas%3C%2Fem%3E%20to%20make%20a%20comment%2C%20even%20after%20you've%20clearly%20said%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20engage%2C%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20let%20it%20derail%20the%20day%2C%20said%20Keisha%20Saunders-Waldron%2C%20a%20licensed%20clinical%20mental%20health%20counselor%20supervisor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20everything%20has%20to%20be%20an%20argument%2C%20especially%20at%20the%20dinner%20table.%20If%20your%20family%20is%20annoying%20you%2C%20but%20not%20saying%20anything%20that%20goes%20against%20your%20values%2C%20Saunders-Waldron%20says%20it's%20OK%20to%20let%20some%20things%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20could%20be%20worth%20hashing%20out%20when%20we're%20talking%20about%20things%20where%20your%20value%20systems%20and%20core%20beliefs%20start%20to%20kick%20in%20%E2%80%94%20but%20if%20we%20know%20there%20is%20no%20resolution%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20worth%20ending%20the%20relationship%20over%2C%20then%20we%20want%20to%20agree%20to%20disagree%2C%26quot%3B%20Saunders-Waldron%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20helps%20to%20set%20firm%20boundaries%20about%20what%20type%20of%20conversation%20you're%20willing%20to%20engage%20in%20ahead%20of%20time%2C%20then%20stick%20to%20them%2C%20Saunders-Waldron%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20And%20remember%3A%20Boundaries%20are%20rules%20you%20make%20about%20your%20own%20behavior%2C%20not%20about%20trying%20to%20control%20someone%20else's.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThose%20boundaries%20can%20sound%20like%20saying%3A%20'I'm%20not%20willing%20to%20continue%20to%20be%20badgered%20right%20now.%20So%20I%20have%20about%20two%20more%20minutes%20to%20talk%20to%20you%20before%20I'm%20walking%20away%2C%20and%20I'm%20giving%20you%20the%20respect%20of%20letting%20you%20know%20that%20I'm%20walking%20away.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224018dbb4-2008-45d3-8f78-9e190048320e%5C%22%3ECheck%20your%20attitude%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20want%20to%20try%20engaging%20in%20a%20conversation%20you%20know%20could%20become%20tense%2C%20the%20easiest%20way%20to%20help%20make%20the%20conversation%20go%20smoothly%20is%20to%20start%20by%20managing%20your%20own%20perspective%2C%20Justin%20Hale%2C%20a%20speaker%20and%20training%20designer%20for%20Crucial%20Learning%2C%20a%20corporate%20training%20company%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOften%2C%20family%20debates%20can%20devolve%20into%20reactionary%20arguments%2C%20where%20people's%20fight-or-flight%20instincts%20get%20triggered.%20Before%20entering%20the%20fray%2C%20remember%20that%20you're%20conversing%20with%20your%20loved%20ones%20%E2%80%94%20not%20fighting%20a%20tiger%20that%20has%20jumped%20out%20of%20the%20bushes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20don't%20go%20into%20a%20discussion%20hoping%20to%20win%20the%20argument%2C%20said%20Vanderbilt%20Professor%20John%20Koch%2C%20senior%20lecturer%20and%20director%20of%20debate.%20If%20that's%20your%20approach%2C%20%26quot%3Byou're%20going%20about%20it%20wrong.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSeek%20understanding%20first%2C%26quot%3B%20Koch%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20winning%20and%20losing%20are%20your%20only%20options%2C%20you're%20missing%20the%20point.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAssume%20the%20person%20you're%20speaking%20to%20has%20good%20intent%2C%20Hale%20added.%20Remind%20yourself%20that%20your%20conversation%20partner%20may%20have%20insight%20into%20the%20topic%20that%20you%20hadn't%20considered%20before%2C%20even%20if%20you%20believe%20they're%20wrong%20in%20their%20opinion.%20Don't%20discount%20the%20idea%20that%20you%20can%20learn%20from%20the%20conversation%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20you're%20just%20learning%20more%20about%20a%20viewpoint%20you%20disagree%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCertainty%20is%20the%20robber%20of%20curiosity.%20The%20more%20certain%20you%20become%2C%20the%20less%20open%20you%20are%20to%20being%20curious%2C%26quot%3B%20Hale%20said.%20%26quot%3BPeople%20are%20afraid%20of%20curiosity%20because%20they're%20worried%20that%2C%20by%20being%20curious%2C%20they%20are%20agreeing%20that%20the%20other%20person%20is%20right%20%E2%80%94%20but%20that's%20absolutely%20not%20true.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2249f2017f-b8eb-4c81-9444-3b27df1ee9e0%5C%22%3ELead%20with%20humor%20and%20humility%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20things%20get%20tense%20despite%20your%20best%20efforts%2C%20it%20can%20be%20helpful%20to%20start%20by%20acknowledging%20that%20everyone%20is%20wrong%20sometimes.%20Being%20humble%20and%20leaning%20into%20humor%20can%20help%20diffuse%20conflict%20before%20it%20escalates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverybody's%20president%20has%20made%20mistakes%2C%26quot%3B%20Hale%20said.%20%26quot%3BEverybody's%20politicians%20have%20been%20wrong.%20And%20nobody%20wants%20to%20admit%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHale%20suggests%20starting%20potentially%20challenging%20conversations%20by%20going%20around%20the%20table%2C%20with%20everyone%20sharing%20something%20they've%20been%20wrong%20about.%20Not%20only%20can%20this%20be%20a%20hilarious%20bonding%20activity%2C%20but%20it%20also%20opens%20the%20door%20for%20everyone%20to%20acknowledge%20they%20could%20be%20wrong%20now%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHaving%20a%20civil%20dialogue%20doesn't%20need%20to%20be%20a%20lost%20art%2C%26quot%3B%20Koch%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20can%20have%20a%20heated%20discussion%20without%20name-calling%20and%20put-downs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20if%20you%20do%20misstep%20and%20find%20yourself%20the%20one%20losing%20your%20temper%2C%20Saunders-Waldron%20said%2C%20it's%20never%20too%20early%20or%20too%20late%20to%20apologize.%20Take%20a%20quick%20walk%20around%20the%20block%20to%20shake%20off%20any%20excessive%20negativity%2C%20then%20try%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTell%20them%3A%20'I%20recognized%20that%20I%20could%20have%20been%20in%20a%20better%20space%20and%20I%20wasn't.%20And%20so%20I%20would%20like%20to%20just%20apologize%20and%20see%20how%20I%20could%20fix%20the%20blunder%2C'%26quot%3B%20Saunders-Waldron%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224bb48a1d-7691-4489-a132-51c93b764a94%5C%22%3EKnow%20when%20to%20cut%20your%20losses%20and%20head%20home%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20it's%20possible%20that%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0despite%20your%20best%20efforts%20%E2%80%94%20the%20conflict%20escalates%20anyway.%20If%20you%20feel%20the%20conversation%20at%20the%20holiday%20event%20cannot%20be%20held%20respectfully%2C%20it's%20also%20fine%20to%20refuse%20to%20engage.%20And%20doing%20so%20thoughtfully%20can%20help%20preserve%20your%20relationships%20while%20clarifying%20your%20values.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20grace%20is%20a%20big%20deal%20in%20this%20whole%20topic%20because%20you%20don't%20want%20to%20alienate%20from%20your%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20Grant%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20still%20give%20everybody%20a%20hug%20on%20the%20way%20out%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20not%20the%20person%20I'm%20pissed%20off%20at%20%E2%80%94%20but%20grandma%2C%20grandpa%2C%20I'd%20say%20'I%20love%20all%20of%20you%20so%20much.%20It%20was%20great%20up%20until%20this%20time%2C%20but%20I%20refuse%20to%20put%20myself%20or%20my%20loved%20ones%20in%20this%20situation.%20Maybe%20we'll%20come%20back%20tomorrow%20and%20see%20you.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20key%20to%20respectfully%20disengaging%20is%20to%20check%20out%20before%20the%20conversation%20becomes%20explosive%2C%20she%20said.%20It%20can%20help%20to%20remember%20that%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20conversation%20is%20important%20to%20you%20because%20you%20value%20the%20relationship%20with%20the%20person%20you're%20arguing%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20do%20it%20with%20love%2C%26quot%3B%20Grant%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20let%20people%20know%20why%20you're%20leaving%2C%20but%20you've%20set%20a%20hard%20boundary%20for%20what%20is%20OK%20and%20what%20is%20not%20OK.%20Because%2C%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20the%20only%20thing%20that%20we%20control%20is%20ourselves%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0I%2