tion%2C%20and%20explosives%20for%20terror%20operatives.%20Naseer%20also%20masterminded%20plots%20to%20facilitate%20his%20own%20escape%20during%20court%20appearances%2C%20a%20plan%20in%20which%20Salman%20was%20a%20player.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20terror%20conspiracy%20was%20uncovered%2C%20Salman%20fled%20India%2C%20evading%20authorities%20until%20his%20arrest%20in%20Rwanda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Salman%20Was%20Arrested%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NIA%20had%20registered%20the%20Bengaluru%20Prisons%20Terror%20Conspiracy%20case%20on%20October%2025%20last%20year%2C%20taking%20over%20from%20Bengaluru%20City%20Police.%20Salman%2C%20already%20declared%20a%20fugitive%2C%20was%20charged%20under%20the%20stringent%20UAPA%2C%20the%20Arms%20Act%2C%20and%20the%20Explosive%20Substances%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Red%20Notice%20was%20issued%20by%20Interpol%20at%20the%20request%20of%20the%20NIA%20on%20August%202%20this%20year.%20Authorities%20in%20Rwanda%2C%20acting%20on%20the%20notice%2C%20arrested%20Salman%20and%20notified%20Indian%20agencies.%20This%20led%20to%20a%20series%20of%20coordinated%20efforts%20between%20the%20NIA%2C%20the%20Rwandan%20National%20Central%20Bureau%20(NCB)%2C%20and%20Interpol%2C%20ultimately%20resulting%20in%20Salman's%20extradition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202024%20alone%2C%2026%20fugitives%20were%20returned%20to%20India%20through%20coordinated%20efforts%20involving%20Interpol.%20These%20include%20individuals%20accused%20of%20crimes%20ranging%20from%20terror%20to%20sexual%20offences%2C%20such%20as%20Raihan%20Arabikkalalarikkal%2C%20wanted%20for%20crimes%20against%20minors%2C%20who%20was%20extradited%20from%20Saudi%20Arabia.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732783980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F8pvet8dg_salman-rehman-khan_650x400_28_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flashkar-terrorist-accused-of-terror-activities-in-be