l%20flying%20in%20Delhi.%20While%20she%20completed%20the%20course%2C%20Aditya%20dropped%20out.%20Srishti%20moved%20to%20Mumbai%20last%20year%20after%20getting%20her%20flying%20license.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tuli%20said%20they%20had%20gone%20through%20Srishti's%20bank%20account%20statement.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20managed%20to%20check%20only%20one%20month's%20statement%20so%20far.%20Around%20Diwali%2C%20about%20Rs%2065%2C000%20was%20transferred%20to%20his%20family%20members.%20I%20am%20convinced%20that%20he%20was%20blackmailing%20her.%20I%20have%20now%20asked%20the%20bank%20for%20the%20whole%20year's%20statement.%20Maybe%2C%20she%20had%20refused%20him%20money%20and%20that%20became%20the%20cause%20of%20her%20death.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAditya%20lives%20in%20Faridabad%20near%20Delhi%20and%20often%20travelled%20to%20Mumbai%20to%20stay%20with%20Srishti.%20%26quot%3BPolice%20are%20saying%20that%20she%20died%20by%20suicide.%20I%20don't%20know%20how%20he%20manipulated%20her%20and%20pushed%20her%20to%20the%20edge.%20What%20did%20he%20do%3F%20She%20spoke%20to%20her%20mother%20and%20aunt%20cheerfully%20just%2015%20minutes%20before%20her%20death.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tuli%20said%20Srishti%20had%20not%20told%20her%20family%20about%20any%20harassment%20she%20was%20facing.%20%26quot%3BShe%20had%20narrated%20bits%20and%20pieces%20to%20her%20sister.%20But%20when%20I%20met%20her%20friends%2C%20they%20told%20me%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20he%20harassed%20her.%20He%20would%20scream%20at%20her%20publicly.%20There%20were%20times%20when%20he%20made%20her%20get%20out%20of%20the%20car%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20road%20and%20drove%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20family%20would%20approach%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Yogi%20Adityanath%20for%20justice.%20%26quot%3BWe%20are%20from%20Gorakhpur.%20I%20would%20go%20and%20request%20Yogi%20ji%20for%20justice.%20I%20cannot%20accept%20that%20she%20died%20by%20suicide.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Tuli%20alleged%20that%20another%20woman%20pilot%20was%20involved%20in%20Srishti's%20death.%20%26quot%3BWe%20came%20to%20know%20that%20another%20woman%20was%20there.%20She%20called%20in%20the%20keymaker%2C%20got%20him%20to%20open%20the%20door%20and%20took%20Srishti%20to%20the%20hospital.%20Who%20opens%20the%20door%20and%20enters%20someone's%20flat%20without%20calling%20the%20cops%3F%20And%20these%20are%20trained%20pilots.%20And%20why%20would%20a%20key%20maker%20randomly%20open%20a%20door%20from%20outside%3F%26quot%3B%20The%20family%20has%20alleged%20that%20Aditya%20also%20pressured%20Srishti%20to%20stop%20eating%20non-vegetarian%20food.%20Recently%2C%20they%20fought%20after%20she%20could%20not%20attend%20his%20sister's%20engagement%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20family%20has%20filed%20a%20complaint%20and%20the%20police%20have%20registered%20an%20FIR%20under%20the%20abetment%20to%20suicide%20charge%20and%20arrested%20Aditya%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ctable%3E%3Cthead%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Cth%20colspan%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3EHelplines%3C%2Fth%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Fthead%3E%3Ctbody%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3EVandrevala%20Foundation%20for%20Mental%20Health%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2B919999666555%5C%22%3E9999666555%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ahelp%40vandrevalafoundation.com%5C%22%3Ehelp%40vandrevalafoundation.com%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%3ETISS%20iCall%3C%2Ftd%3E%3Ctd%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22tel%3A%2B912225521111%5C%22%3E022-25521111%3C%2Fa%3E%20(Monday-Saturday%3A%208%20am%20to%2010%20pm)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%20%3Ctr%3E%3Ctd%20colspan%3D%5C%222%5C%22%3E(If%20you%20need%20support%20or%20know%20someone%20who%20does%2C%20please%20reach%20out%20to%20your%20nearest%20mental%20health%20specialist.)%3C%2Ftd%3E%3C%2Ftr%3E%3C%2Ftbody%3E%3C%2Ftable%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732778640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Ffd275aio_pilot-bf_625x300_28_November_24.j