r%20scrutiny%20for%20chemicals%20in%20their%20clothing.%3Cp%3ERodrigo%20Arangua%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3ESouth%20Korean%20officials%20found%20that%20children's%20clothes%20from%20Temu%20and%20AliExpress%20contained%20toxic%20substances.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EMany%20fashion%20brands%20use%20toxic%20chemicals%20like%20PFAS%20and%20phthalates%2C%20which%20have%20come%20under%20increasing%20scrutiny.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EConsumers%20face%20less%20risk%20getting%20sick%20from%20these%20ingredients%20in%20clothing%20than%20textile%20plant%20workers%20do.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEditor's%20note%3A%20This%20list%20was%20first%20published%20in%20August%202022%20and%20has%20been%20updated%20to%20reflect%20recent%20developments%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChinese%20fast-fashion%20companies%20are%20coming%20under%20renewed%20scrutiny%20for%20toxic%20chemicals%2C%20a%20problem%20that%20has%20plagued%20the%20fashion%20industry%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftemu-children-clothes-contained-622-toxic-limit-seoul-2024-11%5C%22%3EKorean%20officials%20said%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20tested%2026%20pieces%20of%20children's%20winter%20wear%20from%20Temu%2C%20AliExpress%2C%20and%20Shein%20and%20found%20that%20seven%20contained%20toxic%20substances%20like%20phthalate%20plasticizers%2C%20lead%2C%20and%20cadmium.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20children's%20jacket%20from%20Temu%20contained%20622%20times%20the%20legal%20limit%20for%20phthalate%20plasticizers%2C%20a%20chemical%20compound%20that%20makes%20plastics%20more%20flexible.%20Spokespeople%20for%20AliExpress%20and%20Temu%20said%20the%20products%20were%20removed%2C%20while%20a%20Shein%20spokesperson%20said%20the%20tested%20products%20were%20in%20compliance%20with%20regulations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%C2%A0%3Ca%20data-mrf-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshein-temu-shoes-11-229-times-legal-limit-toxic-substances-2024-8%5C%22%20data-mrf-recirculation-id%3D%5C%22Article%20links_2%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%2280%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fshein-temu-shoes-11-229-times-legal-limit-toxic-substances-2024-8%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enot%20the%20first%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%20South%20Korea%20has%20found%20toxic%20chemicals%20in%20items%20from%20Chinese%20fast-fashion%20brands.%20In%20August%2C%20the%20Seoul%20Metropolitan%20Government%20found%20phthalates%20in%20some%20pairs%20of%20shoes%2C%20with%20one%20particular%20pair%20containing%20229%20times%20the%20legal%20limit.%20The%20same%20investigation%20revealed%20that%20sandal%20insoles%20sold%20by%20Temu%20contained%2011%20times%20more%20lead%20than%20legally%20permissible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20in%20an%20earlier%20investigation%20in%20May%2C%20Seoul%20officials%20said%20that%20they%20tested%20a%20pair%20of%20Shein%20shoes%2C%20and%20found%20that%20it%20contained%20428%20times%20the%20permitted%20levels%20of%20phthalates%2C%20according%20to%20the%C2%A0%3Ca%20data-mrf-link%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.straitstimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Fsouth-korea-finds-high-levels-of-toxic-chemicals-in-shein-products%5C%22%20data-mrf-recirculation-id%3D%5C%22Article%20links_3%5C%22%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%20noopener%5C%22%20data-analytics-post-depth%3D%5C%22100%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.straitstimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Fsouth-korea-finds-high-levels-of-toxic-chemicals-in-shein-products%5C%22%20data-analytics-product-module%3D%5C%22body_link%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAFP%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExperts%20said%20that%20many%20large%20clothing%20brands%20like%20Lululemon%2C%20Old%20Navy%2C%20and%20REI%20have%20been%20found%20to%20contain%20toxic%20chemicals%20in%20their%20clothes.%20While%20these%20chemicals%20are%20used%20at%20relatively%20low%20levels%2C%20exposure%20to%20toxic%20substances%20over%20time%20can%20elevate%20a%20person's%20risks%20of%20serious%20health%20conditions%2C%20such%20as%20asthma%20and%20kidney%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20just%20people%20are%20exposed%20to%20one%20on%20a%20regular%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20Alexandra%20McNair%20Quinn%2C%20a%20chemical%20sustainability%20consultant%20and%20founder%20of%20Fashion%20FWD%2C%20a%20nonprofit%20educating%20consumers%20about%20toxic%20chemicals%20in%20clothes%2C%20told%20BI%20in%202022.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20the%20accumulation%20of%20all%20of%20these%20exposures%20in%20a%20regular%20day%20can%20be%20very%20harmful.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EWhy%20chemicals%20are%20so%20pervasive%20in%20fashion%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20use%20of%20chemicals%20like%20PFAS%20and%20lead%20is%20%26quot%3Bfairly%20common%26quot%3B%20within%20the%20fashion%20industry%2C%20Marty%20Mulvihill%2C%20a%20general%20partner%20with%20Safer%20Made%2C%20a%20venture%20capital%20fund%20that%20invests%20in%20firms%20reducing%20exposure%20to%20harmful%20chemicals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYoga%20pants%20and%20gym%20leggings%20sold%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoga-pants-may-contain-toxic-chemicals-linked-to-cancer-lab-2022-1%5C%22%3ELululemon%20and%20Old%20Navy%3C%2Fa%3E%20contained%20PFAS%2C%20according%20to%20testing%20done%20by%20consumer%20health%20activist%20blog%C2%A0Mamavation.%20Outdoor%20apparel%20brands%20Columbia%2C%20REI%2C%20and%20L.L.%20Bean%20received%20either%20a%20D%20or%20F%20grading%20for%20PFAS%20by%20Fashion%20FWD%2C%20a%20non-profit%20educating%20consumers%20about%20toxic%20chemicals%20in%20clothes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(In%202022%2C%20REI%20and%20L.%20L.%20Bean%20reiterated%20their%20commitment%20to%20product%20safety%20in%20statements%20to%20BI.%20Columbia%2C%20Lululemon%2C%20Old%20Navy%2C%20and%20Shein%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20BI's%20requests%20for%20comment%20at%20the%20time.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%202012%20sample%20of%20clothes%20from%20popular%20retailers%20detected%20phthalates%20in%2031%20garments%2C%20and%20lead%20had%20been%20found%20in%20baby%20bibs%20sold%20in%20Walmart%20and%20Babies%20R%20Us%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftoxic-chemicals-in-clothes-cancer-2019-7%23lead-has-been-discovered-in-baby-bibs-3%5C%22%3EBI%20previously%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EQuinn%20said%20manufacturers%20can%20add%20these%20chemicals%20to%20make%20them%20waterproof%20or%20stain-resistant%2C%20and%20soften%20ink%20on%20screen%20prints.%20Lead%20is%20sometimes%20found%20in%20low-cost%20pigments%20and%20inks%2C%20as%20well%20as%20zippers%2C%20and%20chromium%20can%20make%20leather%20more%20pliable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EExposure%20to%20toxic%20chemicals%20builds%20up%20over%20time%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224519%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22People%20in%20a%20textile%20factory%20in%20Bangladesh%20work%20on%20making%20clothing%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F62fe8ba6f1df7e0018eb2d0d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223389%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWorkers%20in%20clothing%20factories%20can%20suffer%20from%20skin%20and%20respiratory%20illnesses%20after%20exposure%20to%20toxic%20chemicals.%3Cp%3EHabibur%20Rahman%20%2F%20Eyepix%20Group%2FFuture%20Publishing%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EExposure%20to%20substances%20like%20lead%20and%20phthalates%20may%20directly%20harm%20people%20manufacturing%20clothes%20more%20than%20consumers%2C%20said%20Scott%20Echols%20in%202022.%20Echols%20is%20a%20senior%20director%20at%20the%20ZDHC%20Foundation%2C%20which%20works%20with%20companies%20to%20limit%20their%20chemical%20footprint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sustainable%20fashion%20analytics%20firm%20Common%20Objective%20estimated%20in%202018%20that%2027%20million%20people%20working%20in%20fashion%20supply%20chains%20worldwide%20might%20suffer%20from%20work-related%20illnesses%20or%20diseases%2C%20including%20skin%20and%20respiratory%20conditions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20the%20exposure%20to%20toxic%20chemicals%20builds%20up%20over%20time%2C%20Quinn%20said.%20Not%20only%20are%20these%20chemicals%20in%20clothing%2C%20they%20exist%20in%20our%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftoxic-chemicals-in-food-pfas-found-by-fda-2019-6%5C%22%3Efood%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fforever-chemicals-pfas-drinking-water-pose-health-risks-small-amounts-2022-6%5C%22%3Ewater%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchemicals-in-shampoo-makeup-linked-to-early-death-study-2021-10%5C%22%3Emakeup%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftoxic-chemical-spreads-cancer-hair-products-for-black-women-2022-6%5C%22%3Epersonal%20care%20products%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPFAS%20don't%20just%20go%20away%2C%20they're%20around%20for%20very%2C%20very%20long%20time%20and%20they're%20very%20harmful%20to%20the%20environment%20and%20to%20human%20health%2C%26quot%3B%20Quinn%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20government%20needs%20to%20develop%20a%20preventative%20approach%20where%20products%20don't%20go%20on%20the%20market%20until%20they're%20proven%20safe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20to%20spot%20chemicals%20in%20clothes%2C%20including%20lead%2C%20flame%20retardants%2C%20and%20'forever%20chemicals'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EQuinn%20told%20BI%20that%20toxic%20chemicals%20used%20to%20make%20clothes%20include%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EChromium%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20used%20in%20leather%20products%20that%20can%20weaken%20the%20immune%20system%20and%20lead%20to%20liver%20and%20kidney%20damage.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchemicals-in-shampoo-makeup-linked-to-early-death-study-2021-10%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPhthalates%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20are%20used%20to%20soften%20the%20ink%20on%20screen%20prints.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-avoid-toxic-chemical-phthalates-in-food-makeup-toiletries-2021-10%5C%22%3EBI's%20Andrea%20Michelson%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20phthalates%20has%20been%20linked%20to%20early%20deaths%20in%20American%20adults%2C%20especially%20due%20to%20heart%20disease%2C%20and%20can%20disrupt%20the%20body's%20hormones.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fendocrine-disruptors-dangerous-chemicals-2019-1%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBrominated%20flame%20retardants%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20are%20sometimes%20found%20in%20children's%20pajamas%20to%20protect%20them%20from%20house%20fires.%20These%20chemicals%2C%20which%20are%20banned%20in%20Europe%2C%20can%20change%20thyroid%20functions%20and%20shift%20the%20way%20the%20body%20processes%20fats%20and%20carbs.%20Researchers%20are%20studying%20whether%20a%20link%20exists%20between%20flame%20retardant%20exposure%20and%20ADHD%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fendocrine-disruptors-dangerous-chemicals-2019-1%5C%22%3EBI%20previously%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-are-pfas-chemicals-2018-8%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EPFAS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20also%20known%20as%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fforever-chemicals-pfas-drinking-water-pose-health-risks-small-amounts-2022-6%5C%22%3Eforever%20chemicals%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20are%20a%20group%20of%20lab-grown%20chemicals%20that%20don't%20break%20down%20in%20the%20environment%20and%20are%20linked%20to%20a%20host%20of%20health%20conditions%20like%20liver%20damage%2C%20asthma%2C%20and%20chronic%20kidney%20disease.%20The%20substance%20is%20water%20resistant%20and%20can%20be%20found%20in%20waterproof%20or%20stain-resistant%20gear%2C%20Quinn%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhalf-of-kids-under-age-6-have-lead-blood-study-2021-9%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3ELead%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20low-cost%20pigment%20or%20sometimes%20used%20as%20a%20cheap%20metal%20for%20zippers.%20Significant%20childhood%20lead%20exposure%20can%20lead%20to%20long-term%20developmental%20problems.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch2%3EHow%20to%20avoid%20chemicals%20in%20clothes%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWashing%20new%20clothing%20is%20an%20important%20step%20in%20reducing%20residual%20substances%2C%20including%20potential%20toxins.%20Use%20hot%20water%20if%20the%20clothes'%20instructions%20allow%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20avoid%20purchasing%20clothing%20with%20PFAS%2C%20check%20your%20label%20for%20materials%20like%20Gore-Tex%20or%20Teflon%2C%20which%20could%20signal%20that%20the%20chemicals%20were%20used%20in%20the%20fabric.%20But%20the%20bigger%20concern%20is%20how%20those%20clothes%20affect%20the%20world%20around%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20biggest%20issue%20associated%20with%20consumer%20products%20isn't%20necessarily%20the%20direct%20exposure%20that%20we%20get%20from%20the%20products%2C%20but%20what%20gets%20released%20into%20the%20environment%20when%20those%20products%20are%20produced%2C%26quot%3B%20Jamie%20DeWitt%2C%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Environmental%20Health%20Sciences%20Center%20at%20Oregon%20State%20University%2C%20told%20BI%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20Laura%20Hardman%2C%20then%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Ocean%20Wise%20Plastic%20Initiative%20at%20the%20Ocean%20Wise%20Plastic%20Lab%20in%20Vancouver%2C%20Canada%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexpert-how-i-keep-baby-family-safe-toxic-plastic-microplastics-2023-1%5C%22%3Etold%20BI%20that%20she%20buys%3C%2Fa%3E%20clothing%20made%20from%20natural%20fibers%20and%20dyes%20for%20her%20and%20her%20child.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20make%20sure%20their%20babies'%20clothes%20are%20organic%2C%20cotton%2C%20and%20made%20with%20child-friendly%20dyes%2C%20but%20they're%20not%20aware%20of%20their%20own%20clothing.%20Your%20baby%20is%20probably%20sucking%20on%20your%20clothes%20more%20than%20she's%20sucking%20on%20hers%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Hardman%2C%20who%20now%20works%20with%20Dubai-based%20consultancy%20Sustainability%20Excellence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftoxic-chemicals-in-shein-and-other-fast-fashion-clothing-2022-8%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732772363000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6747fad7ede4eeae392a362e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftoxic-chemicals-in-shein-and-other-fast-fashion-clothing-2022-8%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20Temu%20kid's%20jacket%20contained%20up%20to%20622%20times%20the%20legal%20limit%20for%20one%20toxin%2C%20per%20Korean%20officials.%20One%20expert%20highlighted%20five%20chemicals%20used%20to%20make%20clothes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Meghan%20Morris%2CAllana%20Akhtar)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A42%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftoxic-chemicals-in-shein-and-other-fast-fashion-clothing-2022-8%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Parliament%20Winter%20Session%20Live%3A%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Takes%20Oath%20As%20Wayanad%20MP%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDay%204%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fparliament-winter-session-from-nov-25-to-dec-20-6948772%5C%22%3EParliament%20Winter%20Session%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0has%20begun%2C%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fby-poll-election-results-2024-live-updates-bypolls-in-48-seats-in-14-states-keralas-wayanad-in-focus-7081398%5C%22%3EPriyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%3C%2Fa%3E%20taking%20oath%20as%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20Kerala's%20Wayanad.%20She