2https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsean-diddy-combs-indictment-allegations-freak-off-sex-performances-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eparticipated%20in%20%26quot%3Bfreak%20offs%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20elaborate%2C%20days-long%20sex%20parties%20that%20Combs%20allegedly%20coerced%20his%20victims%20into%20joining%2C%20according%20to%20other%20court%20filings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20during%20his%20more%20than%20two%20months%20in%20jail%2C%20Combs%20continued%20to%20try%20to%20influence%20witnesses%20and%20prospective%20jurors%2C%20at%20times%20through%20unauthorized%20three-way%20calls%20or%20by%20paying%20other%20inmates%20to%20use%20their%20phone%20access%2C%20the%20judge%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20willingness%20to%20skirt%20BOP%20rules%20in%20a%20way%20that%20would%20make%20it%20more%20difficult%20for%20his%20communications%20to%20be%20monitored%20is%20strong%20evidence%20that%20the%20Court%20cannot%20be%20reasonably%20assured%20as%20to%20the%20sufficiency%20of%20any%20conditions%20of%20release%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20wrote%2C%20using%20the%20acronym%20for%20the%20federal%20Bureau%20of%20Prisons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20especially%20troubling%2C%20the%20judge%20added%2C%20that%20Combs%20tried%20to%20skirt%20BOP%20regulations%20while%20he%20was%20seeking%20bail%2C%20%26quot%3Band%20when%20he%20knew%20the%20government's%20concerns%20about%20witness%20tampering%20and%20obstruction%20were%20front%20and%20center.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20September%2C%20two%20other%20judges%20%E2%80%94%20a%20magistrate%20judge%2C%20and%20Combs'%20previous%20case%20judge%20%E2%80%94%20had%20rejected%20bail%20out%20of%20similar%20concerns%20over%20violence%20and%20potential%20witness%20tampering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECombs%20had%20hoped%20his%20home%20for%20the%20next%20eight%20or%20so%20months%20%E2%80%94%20as%20he%20awaited%20and%20then%20submitted%20to%20a%20federal%20sex-trafficking%20trial%20%E2%80%94%20would%20be%20a%20four-bedroom%2C%20single-fam