sonnel%2C%20Combs'%20defense%20promised.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPreparing%20for%20a%20May%205%20trial%20date%20was%20%26quot%3Bimpossible%26quot%3B%20from%20his%20current%20housing%2C%20the%20federal%20Metropolitan%20Detention%20Center%20in%20Brooklyn%2C%20his%20lawyers%20had%20also%20argued.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20have%20accused%20Combs%20of%20breaking%20federal%20Bureau%20of%20Prison%20rules%20as%20recently%20as%20this%20week%20by%20trying%20to%20influence%20potential%20witnesses%20and%20jurors%20from%20jail%2C%20including%20through%20forbidden%20messaging%20apps%20and%20three-way%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDefense%20lawyers%20had%20countered%20that%20they%20could%20keep%20Combs%20just%20as%20secure%20on%20home%20confinement%20%E2%80%94%20or%20even%20more%20secure%20%E2%80%94%20than%20in%20the%20jail%20where%20he's%20lived%20since%20his%20September%2016%20arrest.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcrisis24.garda.com%2Fabout-us%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20Probation%20and%20Pretrial%20Services%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20federal%20prosecutors%20had%20opposed%20his%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECombs%20has%20pleaded%20not%20guilty.%20His%20lawyers%20have%20said%20in%20court%20and%20in%20filings%20that%20the%20sexual%20behavior%20alleged%20in%20the%20indictment%20was%20consensual%2C%20and%20that%20his%20accusers%20have%20financial%20incentive%20to%20implicate%20him.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EAn%20attorney%20for%20Combs%20declined%20to%20comment%20on%20the%20bail%20denial.%20A%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20US%20Attorney's%20Office%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20on%20the%20bail%20denial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fembed.documentcloud.org%2Fdocuments%2F25419393-us-v-combs-3rd-bail-denial-20241127%2F%3Fembed%3D1%26responsive%3D1%26title%3D1%5C%22%20width%