ref%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.shutterstock.com%2Fimage-photo%2Fghaziabad-uttar-pradesh-indiamarch-15-2022-2136226669%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ER%3C%2Fa%3E)%3B%20For%20representational%20purposes%20only%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElon%20Musk%20recently%20praised%20India%E2%80%99s%20swift%20and%20efficient%20election%20process%2C%20marvelling%20at%20our%20country%E2%80%99s%20ability%20to%20count%20over%20640%20million%20votes%20in%20just%20one%20day.%20Here%E2%80%99s%20a%20breakdown%20of%20how%20this%20incredible%20vote-counting%20process%20unfolds%20in%20India%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E1.%20Counting%20of%20postal%20ballots%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20begins%20with%20the%20counting%20of%20postal%20ballots%2C%20as%20mandated%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India.%20This%20change%20was%20implemented%20after%20irregularities%20during%20the%202019%20elections%2C%20where%20improper%20procedures%20in%20some%20constituencies%20led%20to%20disputes%20in%20closely%20contested%20regions.%20Postal%20ballots%20are%20typically%20cast%20by%20service%20voters%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20members%20of%20the%20armed%20forces%20and%20government%20employees%20posted%20abroad%20%E2%80%94%20and%20other%20eligible%20voters%20unable%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F350690%2Felection-nisarga-grand-hotel-bengaluru-serves-free-dosas-to-people-who-vote-sp-krishnaraj%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evote%20in%20perso%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F350690%2Felection-nisarga-grand-hotel-bengaluru-serves-free-dosas-to-people-who-vote-sp-krishnaraj%2F%5C%22%3En%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Fbetapadhaodeshjagao%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22BetaPadhaoDeshJagao%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FBetaPadhaoDeshJagao-desktop-1732080268.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E2.%20Secure%20transportation%20to%20counting%20centres%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20polling%20day%2C%20Electronic%20Voting%20Machines%20(EVMs)%20and%20Voter%20Verifiable%20Paper%20Audit%20Trail%20(VVPAT)%20units%20are%20securely%20transported%20to%20designated%20counting%20centres%20across%20the%20country.%20These%20machines%20are%20stored%20in%20sealed%20strongrooms%20under%20tight%20security%20until%20counting%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E3.%20Unsealing%20of%20EVMs%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F241695%2Fbihar-india-votes-recount-candidate-evm-returning-officer-fraud-election-assembly-usa-donald-trump-joe-biden-bulletin-vid01%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecounting%20day%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20strongrooms%20housing%20the%20EVMs%20are%20unsealed%20in%20the%20presence%20of%20representatives%20from%20all%20political%20parties%20and%20the%20Returning%20Officer%20(RO)%2C%20ensuring%20transparency.%20The%20counting%20begins%20with%20the%20unsealing%20of%20the%20EVMs%2C%20adhering%20to%20strict%20protocols%20to%20maintain%20fairness.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E4.%20Counting%20in%20rounds%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECounting%20takes%20place%20in%20a%20single%20large%20hall%20equipped%20with%2014%20tables%2C%20each%20assigned%20to%20a%20specific%20constituency.%20In%20every%20round%2C%20votes%20cast%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F107571%2Fm3-evm-2019-lok-sabha-elections%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E14%20EVMs%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20counted%20%E2%80%94%20one%20EVM%20per%20table.%20Once%20the%20votes%20are%20tallied%2C%20the%20results%20for%20that%20round%20are%20immediately%20displayed%20and%20recorded%20on%20a%20blackboard%20attached%20to%20each%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20system%20ensures%20complete%20transparency%20and%20allows%20representatives%20to%20verify%20the%20results%20in%20real-time.%20Subsequent%20rounds%20only%20begin%20after%20the%20results%20of%20the%20previous%20round%20are%20confirmed.%20The%20RO%20supervises%20the%20entire%20process%2C%20ensuring%20that%20it%20is%20conducted%20systematically%20and%20in%20compliance%20with%20election%20protocols.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20612px)%20100vw%2C%20612px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fistockphoto-1217030212-612x612-1-1732521800.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22612%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20counting%20of%20votes%20begin%20with%20the%20counting%20of%20post%20ballots%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fistockphoto-1217030212-612x612-1-1732521800.jpg%20612w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fistockphoto-1217030212-612x612-1-1732521800-300x200.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fistockphoto-1217030212-612x612-1-1732521800-500x333.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2Fistockphoto-1217030212-612x612-1-1732521800-150x100.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-382441%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22408%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20counting%20of%20votes%20begin%20with%20the%20counting%20of%20post%20ballots%20(This%20picture%20is%20sourced%20from%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.istockphoto.com%2Fphoto%2Fcounting-ballot-papers-gm1217030212-355094217%3Fsearchscope%3Dimage%252Cfilm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EiStock%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20representational%20purposes%20only)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E5.%20VVPAT%20verification%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20enhance%20transparency%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20of%20India%20(ECI)%20mandates%20that%20five%20randomly%20selected%20EVMs%20per%20constituency%20undergo%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F182575%2Fvote-general-elections-india-youth-right%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVVPAT%20verification%3C%2Fa%3E.%20During%20this%20process%2C%20the%20VVPAT%20system%20generates%20a%20paper%20slip%20for%20each%20vote%20cast%2C%20which%20can%20be%20cross-checked%20with%20the%20electronic%20results%20from%20the%20EVM.%20If%20discrepancies%20arise%2C%20the%20paper%20slips%20are%20considered%20final.%20This%20step%20guarantees%20the%20accuracy%20and%20integrity%20of%20the%20voting%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E6.%20Consolidation%20of%20results%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20all%20rounds%20of%20counting%20are%20complete%2C%20the%20results%20from%20all%20counting%20tables%20are%20consolidated.%20The%20RO%20then%20declares%20the%20final%20result%20for%20each%20constituency%2C%20including%20the%20total%20number%20of%20votes%20received%20by%20each%20candidate.%20These%20results%20are%20thoroughly%20checked%20for%20any%20discrepancies%20or%20anomalies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E7.%20Submission%20of%20results%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20final%20tally%2C%20the%20results%20are%20sent%20to%20the%20ECI%20for%20official%20records.%20This%20step%20ensures%20the%20official%20compilation%20and%20validation%20of%20the%20election%20data.%20The%20ECI%20oversees%20the%20verification%20of%20all%20results%20and%20ensures%20that%20all%20records%20are%20securely%20archived%20for%20future%20reference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E8.%20Sealing%20of%20EVMs%20and%20VVPATs%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20the%20results%20are%20declared%2C%20the%20EVMs%20and%20VVPAT%20units%20are%20resealed%20and%20stored%20securely%20at%20the%20counting%20centres.%20These%20machines%20are%20retained%20for%20potential%20future%20verification%20or%20recounting%20and%20can%20be%20inspected%20if%20necessary.%20This%20ensures%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20transparent%20recount%20process%20should%20any%20concerns%20arise%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E9.%20Official%20declaration%20of%20results%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20results%2C%20including%20the%20total%20number%20of%20votes%20each%20candidate%20has%20received%2C%20are%20officially%20declared%20by%20the%20RO.%20The%20ECI%20then%20compiles%20these%20results%20from%20all%20constituencies%20and%20announces%20them%20to%20the%20public%2C%20typically%20by%20evening%2C%20once%20the%20counting%20and%20validation%20processes%20are%20complete.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Findia-vote-election-counting-modi-1908222%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newsweek.com%2Findia-vote-election-counting-modi-1908222%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHow%20India%20Counted%20640%20Million%20Votes%20in%20a%20Day%3C%2Fa%3E%3A