n%20encouraging.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20kind%20of%20knew%20what%20menstruation%20was.%20But%20earlier%2C%20I%20used%20to%20feel%20hesitant%20to%20speak%20about%20these%20things%2C%20especially%20at%20home.%20I%20used%20to%20feel%20that%20maybe%20this%20is%20something%20that%20is%20supposed%20to%20be%20kept%20a%20secret.%20But%20then%20when%20we%20saw%20our%20teachers%2C%20and%20people%20from%20Prazna%2C%20speak%20about%20these%20things%2C%20that%20hesitancy%20has%20gone%20away%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Sonali%2C%20a%20Class%2010%20student%20from%20Jaipur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20its%20grassroots%20work%2C%20Prazna%20also%20advocates%20for%20comprehensive%20national%20policies.%20While%20there%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20programmes%20which%20distribute%20pads%2C%20Preeti%20believes%20that%20menstrual%20education%20needs%20to%20go%20beyond%20just%20providing%20products.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20good%20to%20give%20pads%2C%20but%20there%20should%20be%20a%20programme%20that%20happens%20at%20least%20every%20few%20weeks%20where%20the%20conversation%20is%20reopened%20and%20there%20is%20a%20continuous%20dialogue.%20Because%20a%20taboo%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20eased%20with%20a%20single%20workshop%2C%E2%80%9D%20Preeti%20concludes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%2C%20All%20images%20courtesy%20Preeti%20Sharma%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732512431000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-20-at-4.29.19-PM_11zon-1732170305.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D381663%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Prazna%20Foundation's%20Project%20Kishori%20is%20breaking%20the%20silence%20around%20menstruation%20in%20Rajasthan%2C%20creating%20safe%20spaces%20for%20young%20girls%20to%20learn%20about%20their%20bodies%2C%20and%20talk%20openly%20about%20their%20menstrual%20health.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Hemlata%20Ch